graph TD
    %% Complex diagram with multiple features
    A[Input] --> B{Validate}
    B -->|valid| C[Process]
    B -->|invalid| D(Error Handler)
    C --> E{More Data?}
    E -->|yes| A
    E -->|no| F[Output]
    D -.-> G[Log Error]
    D ==> H[Notify Admin]
    G & H --> I[Cleanup]
    I --> F
